.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts, mystery, spy, zombie
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: crimemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
There 5 different types of food: cucumber, cabbage, kiwi, papaya, strawberry
1. the british is the person watching mystery movies
2. the swedish is the person eating kiwi
3. the danish is the person drinking tea
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person drinking coffee
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person eating cabbage
7. the person watching zombie movies is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber
11. the person eating strawberrys is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the crimemaster-smoker is the person drinking beer
13. the german is the prince-smoker
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Movie-Genre		|    zombie	|     crime	|      mystery	|     martial-arts	|     spy	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Food		|     cucumber	|    strawberry	|     cabbage	|     papaya	|      kiwi	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   crimemaster	|
